title: Wilson's Tales of the Borders and of Scotland, Volume 14
author: Various
snippet: We reached the falls ofLubdearg. I parted with Eliza Stewart; and we never met again, as, in afew days afterwards, I left the island; and with this event terminatedall connecting circumstances on my part with "The Skean Dhu."
